name: Smol Youngster Dive
description: Smol version of my photograph from 2014. In Paxos island i have a favorite spot where i usually go and have my afternoon dip in the sea water. Swimming and beach activities of all sorts are part of everyday life for an islander. One of those activities is best dive competition. Such is the case here ; a friend of mine is diving from the edge of the rocks, while an other friend is in the sea. George Angelis 2021. water.
